default million of the £10 million Invest and Contract Readiness Fund to support social ventures seeking social investment or large contracts; and backing the first four social incubators to support social venture start-ups through the £10 million Social Incubator Fund with further awards to be announced early 2014. All of which has driven competition, innovation and quality leading to improvements in public services. 
